OL,3,CThames Water warns it will run out of
OL,4,Cmoney by next May
OL,6,FThames Water has confirmed it has
OL,7,Fenough reserves to keep it afloat
OL,8,Funtil next May but that it needs new
OL,9,Finvestment.
OL,11,FThe water company is creaking under a
OL,12,Fdebt pile of more than #15 billion but
OL,13,Fsaid it has #1.8 billion of liquidity,
OL,14,Fenough to fund its operations for
OL,15,Fanother 10 months.
OL,17,FHowever, despite the constraints, it
OL,18,Fpaid two fresh dividends worth #158.3
OL,19,Fmillion in March, and said it is
OL,20,Funlikely to raise fresh funds before
OL,21,FDecember.
