OL,3,CThames Water warns it will run out of
OL,4,Cmoney by next May
OL,6,FUnder new rules introduced last year,
OL,7,Fwater companies with poor financial
OL,8,Fand environmental records are not
OL,9,Fallowed to pay dividends.
OL,11,FThames Water paid a total of #196
OL,12,Fmillion in dividends last year.
OL,14,FLiberal Democrat Treasury spokesperson
OL,15,FSarah Olney MP said: "This is a
OL,16,Fcomplete mess and it's time the
OL,17,Fregulator started blocking Thames
OL,18,FWater's planned dividend payouts and
OL,19,Feye-watering bill hikes.
