OL,6,FThames Water said profit increased to
OL,7,F#75.4 million for the year ending
OL,8,FMarch 31, up on a #30 million loss the
OL,9,Fyear before.
OL,11,FRevenue increased 11% to #2.5 billion.
OL,13,FPollution incidents increased to 350,
OL,14,Fup on 331 last year, which it blamed
OL,15,Fon a rainier-than-expected year.
OL,17,FThe number of "serious pollutions"
OL,18,Fdecreased by 18%, Thames Water said.
