OL,3,CThames Water warns it will run out of
OL,4,Cmoney by next May
OL,6,FIt said it spent #2 billion on
OL,7,Fmaintaining and updating its
OL,8,Finfrastructure last year.
OL,10,FThe financial update will be followed
OL,11,Fon Thursday by a draft verdict from
OL,12,FOfwat on water companies' five-year
OL,13,Fspending plans and bill increases to
OL,14,F2030.
OL,16,FThat will kick off six months of
OL,17,Fnegotiations with Ofwat, ahead of its
OL,18,Ffinal decision in December.
